Class RouteResponse

java.lang.Object
  com.mapquest.android.maps.ServiceResponse
      com.mapquest.android.maps.RouteResponse

public class RouteResponse
extends ServiceResponse

This class is an object representation of a directions service response see Directions Service Documentation for more information. Attributes returned from the Directions service may not exist in this wrapper, you can get the raw json response from ServiceResponse.serviceResponse field.
